Prima Interactive has announced the South African release date for the Xbox One X. The console will be available at retailers across the country from 22 December 2017. A limited number of BT Games customers who pre-ordered the Xbox One X will receive the Xbox One X Scorpio Edition at no extra cost. The Scorpio Edition upgrades were applied on a first-paid, first-served basis following the launch of Xbox One X pre-orders. The Xbox One X boasts powerful hardware which delivers 4K gaming and video in addition to HDR support.